==Starting off==
* '''Player:''' Hello Easter Bunny. How're things?
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Hello there [player name]. It's nice to see you, though things could certainly be better...
* '''Player:''' Oh, what's the matter?
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Interest in chocolate eggs is dwindling, [player name]. We're trying to spark some new life into them but can't quite manage it.
* '''Player:''' What have you tried to do to increase interest so far?
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Well, we thought some new and unique flavours might do it, so my son Chocco has been investigating but he's not been able to find the right flavours.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Maybe I could help out?}}
** '''Player:''' Maybe I could help out?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' That's very kind of you [player name], I'm sure Chocco would appreciate all the help he can get.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' He's operating out of our new location on Wester Island. The only way to get there is through the rabbit tunnel network.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Simply hop into the large rabbit hole just here and go straight ahead, take the third right, seventh left and you should arrive right there.
** '''Player:''' Third right, seventh left. Got it. I'll get going then!
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Thanks, [player name]!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'm sure you'll work it out.}}
** {{tmissing}}

