==Talking to Chocco==
* '''Player:''' Hello, you must be Chocco, your father asked me to assist you in creating new flavours, how can I help?
* '''Chocco:''' Oh did he? Good to know he doesn't think I can do it...
* '''Player:''' I'm sure he believes in you but we all need help every now and again...
* '''Chocco:''' Fine... I might as well make use of you while you're here... we need some new flavours, can you do that?
* '''Player:''' Certainly, what flavour would you like me to create?
* '''Chocco:''' I want you to make me a [Fruity/Fresh/Bitter/Earthy/Smoked/Crunchy/Spicy/Fishy/Meaty/Rich/Fluffy/Salted] easter egg.
* '''Chocco:''' My assistant Milkee is in the cavern, he should be able to help you make eggs.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Chocco again===
* '''Player:''' What am I supposed to be doing again?
* '''Chocco:''' I want you to make me a [Fruity/Fresh/Bitter/Earthy/Smoked/Crunchy/Spicy/Fishy/Meaty/Rich/Fluffy/Salted] easter egg.
