==Chocco's taste testing==
===Talking to Chocco with an egg===
* '''Player:''' I've made you an egg.
* '''Chocco:''' Give it to me so I can taste it then please.
* {{tact|end}}

===Using an egg on Chocco===
* {{tbox|pic=Crunchy easter egg detail.png|The Wester Bunny devours the egg and almost your hand as you pass it over.}}
* {{tcond|If the flavour isn't what he wanted:}}
** '''Chocco:''' No no no... this is all wrong! You've not captured the flavour I wanted at all.
** '''Chocco:''' Please try again and make me a [Fruity/Fresh/Bitter/Earthy/Smoked/Crunchy/Spicy/Fishy/Meaty/Rich/Fluffy/Salted] easter egg.
** '''Player:''' Okay, sorry.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the flavour is what he wanted:}}
** '''Chocco:''' Oh yes! You've definitely captured the flavour I wanted but I don't think it's the right flavour for our customers.
** {{tcond|First three flavours tested:}}
*** '''Player:''' Oh okay, should I make you a different flavoured chocolate egg?
*** '''Chocco:''' Yes please, I would like to try a [Fruity/Fresh/Bitter/Earthy/Smoked/Crunchy/Spicy/Fishy/Meaty/Rich/Fluffy/Salted] easter egg.
*** '''Player:''' Okay, I'll see what I can do.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|After testing the fourth flavour:}}
*** '''Chocco:''' This is useless, all of these flavours are terrible! Thanks for nothing, get off our island!
*** {{mes|Chocco knocks you out and throws you out to sea.}}
*** {{mes|You manage to swim your way back to Rimmington.}}
*** {{mes|The Wester Bunnies relieve you of their supplies as you leave the island.}}
*** '''Player:''' Ungrateful bunnies... I'd better go and tell the Easter Bunny what happened...
*** {{tact|end}}

==Finishing up==
* '''Player:''' I tried to help your son but he kicked me off of Wester Island!
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Oh? That's okay... I guess I didn't need help after all! Chocco has created four new flavours of Easter egg and they're wildly popular!
* '''Player:''' Wait! I created those flavour profiles!
* '''Easter Bunny:''' But I thought you just said you didn't help?
* '''Player:''' Chocco asked me to create some new flavours, which I did, then he called me useless and threw me into the sea!
* '''Easter Bunny:''' That doesn't sound like Chocco.. Oh well, if you did help, thanks!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Wait a minute... Thanks? That's it?}}
** '''Player:''' Wait a minute... Thanks? That's it?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' What else did you expect, [player name]?
** '''Player:''' A reward of some kind for all my hard work, you're clearly reaping the benefits.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' We didn't contractually agree upon any rewards before you agreed to help, and I'm not even certain that you did help.
** '''Player:''' I slaved away in your little factory and for my trouble I get thrown into the sea...
** '''Easter Bunny:''' So it would seem, perhaps you've learned a valuable lesson [player name].
** '''Player:''' Perhaps... And perhaps the recipes for your new flavours could be of value to your competitors. Goodbye.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Wait! Hold on... Thank you for all your hard work [player name].
** {{tbox|pic=Easter egg helm detail.png|pic2=Easter egg detail.png|The Easter Bunny hands you some chocolate eggs and an egg shaped helm.}}
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Please accept these gifts as a small token of my appreciation.
** '''Player:''' Thank you!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|You're welcome?}}
** '''Player:''' You're welcome I guess? See you around...
** {{tact|Talking to the Easter Bunny again after selecting this dialogue will automatically start from "Wait a minute... Thanks? That's it?"}}
** {{tact|end}}

